♪ That's right ♪

02:04.680 --> 02:05.713
♪ Whenever this life
gets tough ♪

02:05.780 --> 02:06.880
♪ You gotta fight with ♪

02:06.946 --> 02:08.113
♪ My homegirls
standing to my left ♪

02:08.180 --> 02:09.346
♪ And my right ♪
♪ True blue ♪

02:09.413 --> 02:10.780
♪ It's tight like glue ♪

